        {
          "id": "6567b2e94d9e_3",
          "href": null,
          "name": "2029",
          "text": "Last week I got an email from friends at the Findhorn ecovillage asking me whether I could write a short blog post about Paul Stamets visit to Findhorn in 2010. The Universal Hall will be one of over 500 venues around the world that will host a screening of Fantastic Fungi. [Note: now online for physical distancing and social connecting while we try to ‘flatten the curve’ and save lives!] This cinematographic masterpiece by the visual poet cameraman and director Louie Schwartzberg is based on Paul’s work. The screening will take place on March 26th and will be followed by an interview on video-link after this global event with Louie Schwartzberg and Paul Stamets.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
